gujarati.context:
Bolya ichchharama rachho, nath hathni maalano kod;
Male prasaadee kyaanthi maulum, maage diyee daya kari dyaal.

translated to:

Spoken words are the desire's path, don't have the hand's code; 
Reach Prasadini from where did the yarn come, having asked give mercy's thread.

Here is the translation:

The words spoken are like an ear, afterwards take pity and give attention; 
He has gone to the understanding of God, spoke with such force that it will not be destroyed.

Here is the translation:

It was a tree in my hand, good branch, my family's fate; 
Fortune gave me bitter cheese, and it did not happen as I wished.

Here is the translation:

We see God's vision in a glimpse, such a moment does not come again; 
The Lord gives us this world, there is no other matter above it.
